<br>
So are the beastlords your sworn enemy despite another pet class having a higher dps pet than beastlords? If you continue that thinking krilen you will be disappointed with the game because we will not be held down in that manner. I do not bitch about mage pets so stop bitching about ours. I know that I will get flamed for this but just remember I did not make the comment about warders never doing the dmg of ANY mage pet. Beastlords are here to stay and the rest of the classes in eq will just have to accept that. We are going to step on someones toes no matter what improvements we get and a lot of the beast community realises this. So we will be defensive about any gains made since we can not please everyone if we hope to be balanced. Are we way out in left field in terms of balance,no but we still have some ways to go.<br>
<br>
