<br>
Tanking: Warder &lt; Water Pet (lvl 60)<br>
Damage: Warder &lt; Water Pet (lvl 60)<br>
<br>
but close in both those categories? Especially the damage category (*we* tank, not our pets...). This would allow us to improve our raid DPS while still having your water pet spank our warder =). Right now as our pets go, I would *gladly* give up a good deal of tanking ability for the chance to do more damage and to realize our OFFENSIVE role in a raid.<br>
<br>
So to finalize.<br>
<br>
Damage: Earth &lt; Air &lt; Warder &lt; Water &lt; Epic<br>
Tanking: Warder &lt; Water &lt; Air &lt; Earth &lt; Epic<br>
<br>
As long as the damage part is close to the water pet, I would be fully happy with this result. Give us less hps, give us less ac, whatever is needed to reduce our pet's tanking ability to compensate.<br>
<br>
